        "generateUrl": "https://support.personio.de/hc/en-us/articles/4404623630993-Generate-and-manage-API-credentials",
        "setup": "In a Personio account, go to `Settings > API credentials` and choose **Generate new credentials**. Personio issues a `client_id` and `client_secret`; use them with the client-credentials token flow at `POST /v2/auth/token` to obtain a bearer token for non-recruiting APIs. Attribute access and scopes are configured in the credential wizard; for employee data you must whitelist the attributes you want to read. See [Get started with Personio API](https://developer.personio.de/docs/getting-started-with-the-personio-api) and [Generate and manage API credentials](https://support.personio.de/hc/en-us/articles/4404623630993-Generate-and-manage-API-credentials)."
      },
